oduct-roadmap/tool-calling-projects/</guid><description>---</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>斯坦福 CS 课程学习图谱：面向 AI 与 LLM 的路线</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/stanford-cs-learning-map/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/stanford-cs-learning-map/</guid><description>把 17 门 Stanford CS 课程按应用、原理、系统三层整理成 AI/LLM 学习路径。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>AIGC 视频学习地图：从 Prompt 到分镜工作流</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/aigc/aigc-video-learning-map/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/aigc/aigc-video-learning-map/</guid><description>整理 AI 视频生成的学习顺序、Prompt 结构、分镜练习、来源边界和版权注意事项。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>AIGC 视频 Prompt 来源库</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/aigc/aigc-video-prompt-sources/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/aigc/aigc-video-prompt-sources/</guid><description>以后需要找 AIGC 视频 prompt、动作 prompt、武侠 prompt、Seedance prompt、随机 prompt 灵感时，优先从这个页面检索，而不是每次从零开始搜网页。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>AIGC 视频 Prompt 模板库</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/aigc/aigc-video-prompt-templates/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/aigc/aigc-video-prompt-templates/</guid><description>这些模板用于写自己的视频，不用于照搬《丧尸清道夫》原始提示词。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>AIGC 视频来源与版权边界</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/aigc/aigc-video-source-copyright/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/aigc/aigc-video-source-copyright/</guid><description>链接：https://github.com/jnMetaCode/ai-shortfilm-prompts</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>AIGC 视频创作工作流与练习</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/aigc/aigc-video-workflow-practice/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/aigc/aigc-video-workflow-practice/</guid><description>每一轮只追求一个进步点：</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>AIGC 国风武侠打斗 Prompt 拆解</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/aigc/aigc-wuxia-fight-prompt/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/aigc/aigc-wuxia-fight-prompt/</guid><description>目前没有找到成熟的“雾山五行逐镜头拉片 + 系统 prompt 库 + skill”的开源项目。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Mx-Shell《丧尸清道夫》方法论</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/aigc/mx-shell-zombie-cleaner-methodology/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/aigc/mx-shell-zombie-cleaner-methodology/</guid><description>把 AI 视频 prompt 写成“分镜导演台本”，而不是写成“风格形容词愿望清单”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>微信小程序开发者学习路径</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/wechat-miniprogram/wechat-miniprogram-developer-roadmap/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/wechat-miniprogram/wechat-miniprogram-developer-roadmap/</guid><description>微信 AI 生态接入要求开发者至少拥有可被微信 AI 调用的小程序业务能力。对个人来说，先成为小程序开发者，才有资格把自己的服务封装成小程序能力，再进一步做 AI Agent 入口。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CS 107: Computer Organization and Systems</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs107-computer-organization-and-systems/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs107-computer-organization-and-systems/</guid><description>计算机系统基础概念：C 语言编程、数据表示、机器级代码、计算机算术、编译、内存组织与管理、性能评估与优化。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CS 146S: The Modern Software Developer</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs146s-the-modern-software-developer/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs146s-the-modern-software-developer/</guid><description>AI 正在快速改变我们构建、调试和维护软件的方式。从 Cursor、Warp 等新一代 IDE 和终端，到 Coderabbit、Qodo 等代码审查和测试平台，软件开发的每个环节都在被重塑。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CS 149: Parallel Computing</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs149-parallel-computing/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs149-parallel-computing/</guid><description>涵盖 GPU、向量指令集、共享/非共享内存、同步机制、MapReduce、Apache Spark、SIMT 等并行编程模型。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CS 221: Artificial Intelligence: Principles and Techniques</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs221-ai-principles-and-techniques/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs221-ai-principles-and-techniques/</guid><description>涵盖搜索、约束满足、博弈、马尔可夫决策过程、概率图模型、机器学习和逻辑。AI 领域的全景入门。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CS 221M: Mechanistic Interpretability</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs221m-mechanistic-interpretability/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs221m-mechanistic-interpretability/</guid><description>理解模型如何处理信息以及为什么产生特定输出的 ML 子领域。涵盖探针（probing）、引导（steering）、因果抽象和稀疏自编码器。包含来自学术界和工业界领先可解释性实验室的客座讲座。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CS 224N: Natural Language Processing with Deep Learning</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs224n-nlp-with-deep-learning/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs224n-nlp-with-deep-learning/</guid><description>自然语言处理（NLP）是信息时代最重要的技术之一。NLP 的应用无处不在：网络搜索、广告、邮件、客服、翻译、虚拟助手、医疗报告等。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CS 224v: Conversational Virtual Assistants with Deep Learning</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs224v-conversational-virtual-assistants/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs224v-conversational-virtual-assistants/</guid><description>聚焦 LLM 在对话系统中的应用： 1. 通过监督学习和自学习增长 LLM 知识 2. 通过外部知识库防止幻觉 3. 处理结构化和非结构化数据</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CS 224w: Machine Learning with Graphs</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs224w-machine-learning-with-graphs/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs224w-machine-learning-with-graphs/</guid><description>涵盖表征学习和图神经网络（GNN）、万维网算法、知识图谱推理、影响力最大化、社交网络分析。学习 PyG（PyTorch Geometric）等图学习工具。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CS 229: Machine Learning</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs229-machine-learning/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs229-machine-learning/</guid><description>涵盖统计模式识别、线性/非线性回归、非参数方法、指数族分布、GLMs、支持向量机、核方法、深度学习、模型/特征选择、学习理论、聚类、密度估计、EM 算法、降维（PCA/ICA）、强化学习与自适应控制、马尔可夫决策过程等。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CS 230: Deep Learning</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs230-deep-learning/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs230-deep-learning/</guid><description>学习深度学习基础、构建神经网络、领导成功的 ML 项目。涵盖 CNN、RNN、LSTM、Adam、Dropout、BatchNorm 等。采用翻转课堂模式，通过医疗、自动驾驶、音乐生成、NLP 等实际案例学习。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CS 231n: Deep Learning for Computer Vision</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs231n-deep-learning-for-computer-vision/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs231n-deep-learning-for-computer-vision/</guid><description>学习实现、训练和调试神经网络，深入了解视觉识别的前沿研究。涵盖学习算法、神经网络架构、训练和微调网络的工程技巧。从 ImageNet 到 ResNet 到 Vision Transformer，覆盖 CNN 的完整演进。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CS 234: Reinforcement Learning</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs234-reinforcement-learning/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs234-reinforcement-learning/</guid><description>涵盖马尔可夫决策过程、RL 基础、大规模域扩展、探索挑战。包含深度强化学习作业。应用于机器人、游戏、消费者建模和医疗保健。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CS 236: Deep Generative Models</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs236-deep-generative-models/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs236-deep-generative-models/</guid><description>涵盖变分自编码器（VAE）、生成对抗网络（GAN）、Flow 模型的概率基础和学习算法。应用于计算机视觉、语音、NLP 和强化学习。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CS 324: Advances in Foundation Models</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs324-advances-in-foundation-models/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs324-advances-in-foundation-models/</guid><description>深入学习基础模型（如 GPT-3、CLIP、Stable Diffusion）的模型与算法、系统与基础设施、伦理与社会影响。学生将获得实践经验，识别基础模型的真实用例。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CS 336: Language Modeling from Scratch</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs336-language-modeling-from-scratch/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs336-language-modeling-from-scratch/</guid><description>语言模型是现代 NLP 应用的基石，为下游任务提供了通用系统的新范式。本课程通过引导学生完成开发自己语言模型的全过程，让学生全面掌握语言模型。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CS 348k: Visual Computing Systems</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs348k-visual-computing-systems/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs348k-visual-computing-systems/</guid><description>研究并行异构系统的设计与挑战，用于执行和加速视觉计算应用（计算摄影、图像/视频理解、实时 3D 图形）。涵盖高效图形、图像处理和计算机视觉系统架构设计。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>CS 349d: AI Inference Infrastructure</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs349d-ai-inference-infrastructure/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/learning/stanford-cs/cs349d-ai-inference-infrastructure/</guid><description>聚焦复合 AI 系统的云计算基础设施和架构模式。客座讲座来自 Databricks、OpenAI、NVIDIA、Microsoft 等公司。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>GitHub Pages vs Vercel：个人博客部署怎么选</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/posts/github-pages-vs-vercel-blog-deploy/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/posts/github-pages-vs-vercel-blog-deploy/</guid><description>从个人博客长期维护角度，对比 GitHub Pages 和 Vercel 的部署模型、能力边界、迁移风险与实际选择。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 May 2026 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Windows 通过 WSL2 部署 vLLM 的关键步骤</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/posts/windows-vllm-wsl2-deploy/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/posts/windows-vllm-wsl2-deploy/</guid><description>整理 Windows 环境下通过 WSL2 部署 vLLM 的架构、依赖、启动方式、显存参考、客户端接入和常见避坑点。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 02:30:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Cherry Studio：本地 AI 客户端与知识库工作流</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/posts/cherry-studio-knowledge-base-guide/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/posts/cherry-studio-knowledge-base-guide/</guid><description>从个人 AI 工作流角度梳理 Cherry Studio 的多模型对话、本地知识库、MCP 扩展、本地模型接入和使用边界。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 02:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>RAG：检索增强生成的工作方式与边界</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/posts/rag-retrieval-augmented-generation/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/posts/rag-retrieval-augmented-generation/</guid><description>用个人知识管理视角解释 RAG 的架构流程、检索质量、适用场景、局限，以及它和 LLM Wiki 的区别。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>LLM Wiki 方法论：让 AI 维护一座可增长的知识库</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/posts/llm-wiki-methodology/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/posts/llm-wiki-methodology/</guid><description>整理 LLM Wiki 的核心思想、目录结构、维护流程和与 RAG 的区别，说明如何把知识库变成可持续增长的系统。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Hexo 博客 + Obsidian：写作组合配置</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/posts/hexo-obsidian-guide/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/posts/hexo-obsidian-guide/</guid><description>记录如何把 Obsidian 作为静态博客写作环境，并统一文章、图片、frontmatter、预览和发布流程。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Feb 2026 06:48:07 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Hexo + GitHub Pages 个人博客搭建</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/posts/hexo-github-blog-setup/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/posts/hexo-github-blog-setup/</guid><description>从 Node.js 环境、Hexo 初始化、GitHub Pages 仓库、部署配置、主题切换到图片管理，完整记录一次个人博客搭建过程。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Feb 2026 06:47:41 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>文章可见性控制演示</title><link>https://shiaoming123.github.io/posts/visibility-control-demo/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://shiaoming123.github.io/posts/visibility-control-demo/</guid><description>演示静态博客中公开、私密、需密码三种文章可见性状态的设计思路、实现方式和安全边界。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Feb 2026 06:20:56 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>